<HEADLINE> Asain Games Tickets to Go on Sale Mid-year </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BANGKOK, March 17 (Xinhua) -- Tickets for the 13th Asian Games
to held in Bangkok in December will go on sale by the middle of
the year, organisers said here on Tuesday.
</P>
<P>
Tickets will range in price from 20 baht (50 cents) for local
students to 5,000 baht (125 U.S. dollars) for the opening and
closing ceremonies.
</P>
<P>
Organisers said they expect to raise 335 million baht (837,500
U.S. dollars) from the sale of about 503,000 tickets.
</P>
<P>
Tickets for the opening and closing ceremonies will be on sale
from July 1 while competition events' tickets will be sold from
September. 
</P>
