<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Bridal Photography Business Withers in Shanghai </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, March 17 (Xinhua) -- The bridal photography business
is withering in Shanghai, with more than 20 such shops
closing.
</P>
<P>
Bridal photography was most prosperous in 1996, with more than
100 companies soliciting newlyweds to take pictures.
</P>
<P>
However, the business declined in 1997. During the second half
of 1997, prices for a bridal photo were reduced by 20 percent.
</P>
<P>
According to a recent survey, overly high prices and an
obsession with making everyone look like stars led to its
unpopularity.
</P>
<P>
 
</P>
</TEXT>
