<TEXT>
<P>
LUANDA, March 17 (Xinhua) -- Under the new agenda for Angolan
peace process and the Lusaka Peace Accord signed in 1994 by
Angola's warring sides, Angolan President Eduardo dos Santos
Monday appointed three governors designated by UNITA.
</P>
