<DOCNO> XIE19980317.0169 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-03-17 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Malaysia Ensures Labuan as Good Financial Center </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KUALA LUMPUR, March 17 (Xinhua) -- Malaysia said Tuesday that
it is determined to ensure that Labuan, a federal territory off
Sabah, East Malaysia, would continue to be a reputable offshore
center for quality and genuine investors.
</P>
<P>
The Labuan International Offshore Financial Center (IOFC),
established in October 1990, is one of the few integrated offshore
financial centers in this region.
</P>
<P>
The financial crisis in the region, together with a slowdown in
the regional economies, would have some adverse effects on certain
types of offshore activities, particularly offshore banking and to
some extent, company incorporation and registration, State Bank
Governor Ahmad Mohd Don said.
</P>
<P>
"Nevertheless, on the part of the government, additional
measures continued to be adopted to establish Labuan as a premier
IOFC," Ahmad was quoted by the Malaysian national news agency
Bernama as saying at a seminar on "Labuan: Malaysia's
International Offshore Financial Center" held in Johor Baharu,
southern Malaysia, Tuesday.
</P>
<P>
Ahmad is also chairman of the Labuan Offshore Financial
Services Authority, which is a regulatory agency set up to handle
the problems investors may have when operating in Labuan.
</P>
<P>
Ahmad said that while many new activities have been introduced
in Labuan, prudential requirements and greater supervision would
be given adequate focus.
</P>
<P>
To this end, he said Labuan has decided to build its offshore
center on a more solid ground through the exercise of prudence and
unwavering commitment toward maintaining a clean reputation.
</P>
<P>
The Labuan IOFC currently offers a full range of offshore
financial services including offshore banking, insurance, trust
business, fund management, investment holding, investment banking
and management services activities.
</P>
<P>
Ahmad said the Labuan IOFC is now in a position to further
consolidate and brace itself for greater challenges this year as
it has made encouraging progress since its establishment, thus
providing a firm foundation for further growth.  
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
