<TEXT>
<P>
TOKYO, March 17 (Xinhua) -- Japanese Defense Agency chief Fumio
Kyuma will pay a five-day visit to China in May for talks with his
Chinese counterpart, Chi Haotian, Kyodo News reported Tuesday.
</P>
