<HEADLINE> Vietnam's Financial Situation Remains Stable </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HANOI, March 16 (Xinhua) -- Although Vietnam has to face many
difficulties caused by the regional financial crisis, the country
has been successfully managed its currency, the Vietnamese dong,
Vietnam News Agency Monday quoted Finance Minister Nguyen Sing
Hung said.
</P>
<P>
The Vietnam News Agency Monday quoted the finance minister as
saying that the success was partly resulted from lessons and
experiences learned from other countries in adjusting the foreign
exchange rate of the domestic currency.
</P>
