currencies, Vietnam has increased its reserve of foreign
currencies to meet the import requirement, the minister said.
</P>
<P>
He noted that Vietnam's foreign currency reserve can ensure
the country's import for many weeks.
</P>
<P>
Prices of farm products and foodstuffs have encouraged farmers
and exporters to promote their activities. 
